(16, 1, '2017-12-14 03:34:58', '2017-12-14 03:34:58', '<h1 class=\"c-heading-2 f-lean article-heading ng-binding ng-scope\">Install Java in Internet Explorer</h1>\r\n<div data-grid=\"col-12 pad-12x\">\r\n<div class=\"main-content-container\" data-grid=\"container\"><header class=\"page-title-header\">\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"c-divider f-pad-bottom-6x f-pad-top-3x\" />\r\n\r\n</header></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-grid=\"col-12 pad-12x\">\r\n<div class=\"main-content-container\" data-grid=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"ng-scope ng-isolate-scope\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"content-article\">\r\n<div class=\"ng-isolate-scope\">\r\n<div class=\"ng-scope\">\r\n<div class=\"ng-isolate-scope\"><section class=\"section ng-scope\">\r\n<div class=\"section-body ng-scope\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"ng-scope col-xs-24\">\r\n<div class=\"ng-isolate-scope\">\r\n<ol class=\"ng-scope\">\r\n 	<li>Open Internet Explorer icon and go to <a class=\"managed-link content-anchor-link\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkID=330247\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-content-id=\"\" data-content-type=\"\" data-bi-name=\"content-anchor-link\" aria-live=\"rude\">Java.com</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Select the <strong>Free Java Download </strong>button, and then select <strong>Agree and Start Free Download</strong>. If you\'re prompted for an administrator password or confirmation, type the password or provide confirmation.</li>\r\n 	<li>On the notification bar, select <strong>Run</strong>. If you\'re prompted for an administrator password or confirmation, type the password or provide confirmation.</li>\r\n 	<li>Select <strong>Install </strong>&gt; <strong>Close</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>If you\'re having problems installing or using Java, look for answers in the <a class=\"managed-link content-anchor-link\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkID=330249\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-content-id=\"\" data-content-type=\"\" data-bi-name